    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(SN) In nomine domini Dei eterni. Anno eiusdem domini nostri Iesu Christi
                        MCXXXI , quinto die exeunte septembris, indicione VIIII. <rs key="#Churches"
                            >Ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Churches #Offersio/donatio #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Legumes #Wine #Hay/fodder #Animals#Forests #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Mills Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Canals"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2075">Sancti Cipriani</orgName> in <placeName
                                key="#Churches" ref="#places/4147">Murane</placeName>, <placeName key="#Geographic_regions" ref="#places/914"
                            >Veneciane</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Geographic_regions">provincie</rs> site. Ego <persName
                            key="#marriage #Roman #Offersio/donatio #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #heirTo #childOf #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Legumes #Wine #Hay/fodder #Animals#Forests #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Mills Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Canals"
                                ><name ref="Berta">Berta</name></persName>, simul cum <rs
                            key="#marriage">iugali</rs> meo <persName
                            key="#marriage #Roman #Offersio/donatio #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Legumes #Wine #Hay/fodder #Animals#Forests #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Mills Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Canals"
                                ><name ref="Dominicus/de Gumpo">Dominico</name></persName> de Gumpo,
                        qui professi sumus nos ex nacione nostra lege vivere <rs key="#Roman"
                            >Romana</rs>, presens presentibus: quisquis in sanctis ac venerabilibus
                        locis allquid de suis rebus contulerit, iuxta auctoris vocis centuplum
                        accipiet, et insuper, quod melius est, vitam possidebit eternam. Ideoque ego
                        quae supra Berta simul cum viro meo Dominico, pro anima nostra et peccatorum
                        nostrorum remissione, dono et offero predicte ecclesie et in eius iure et
                        proprietate per hanc <rs key="#Offersio/donatio">cartulam offersionis</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">proprietario nomine</rs>, in eam
                        ad habendum confirmo, ideoque quicquid ego habere et possidere visa sum in
                            <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/3715"><rs key="#Comitatus"
                                >comitatu</rs>
                            <placeName
                                key="#Comitatus #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Legumes #Wine #Hay/fodder #Animals #Forests #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Mills Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Canals"
                                ref="#places/4418">Saccisico</placeName></geogName>, scilicet res
                        immobiles ex parte et <rs key="#heirTo">successione</rs>
                        <persName key="#parentOf"><name ref="Andreas/Saurelius">Andree
                                Saureli</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">patris</rs> mei advenientes, cum omnibus rebus ad
                        predictas <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terras</rs> pertinentibus, scilicet
                        curn <rs key="#Landed_possessions">areis</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Cereals #Legumes">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder"
                            >pratis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder #Animals">pascuis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Forests">silvis</rs>, stellareis, rupis, rupinis ac <rs
                            key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">paludibus</rs>, <rs key="#Mills"
                            >molendinis</rs>, <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >piscationibus</rs>, <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >venationibus</rs>, cultis et incultis, divisis et indivisis, una cum
                        finibus, terminis, accessionibus et <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">usibus aquarum</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Canals">aquarumque ductibus</rs>, cum omni iure adiacentibus et
                        pertinentibus eisdem rebus in integrum. Quam autem supradictam offersionem
                        iuris meis superius dicta, una cum accessione et ingressu seu cum
                        superioribus et inferioribus suis qualiter superius legitur in integrum ab
                        hac die predicte ecclesie Sancti Cipriani dono et offero ac per presentem
                        cartulam offersionis in eam ad habendum confirmo, ut administratores et
                        eorum successores faciant a presenti die quicquid voluerint, quod tamen non
                        sit contra leges, sine omni nostra et heredum nostrorum contradictione. Et
                        quidem spondeo atque promitto me quae supra Berta, simul cum viro meo
                        nostrisque heredes, predictam offersionem qualiter supra legitur in integrum
                        ab omni homine defensare; quod si defendere non potuerimus aut si exinde
                        aliquid quovis ingenio subtrahere quaesierimus, tunc <rs key="#Penalty">in
                            duplum</rs> eandem offersionem restituamus sicut pro tempore fuerit
                        meliorata aut valuerit, sub estimacione in consimilibus rebus. Nec michi
                        liceat nolle quod factum est et volui, sed quod a nobis semel factum vel
                        conscriptum est inviolabiliter conservare promittimus cum stipulacione
                        subnixa. Actum est in <rs key="#Villas">villa</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Villas">Carpini</placeName>. Feliciter. Signa manuum
                        ++++++++ supradictorum Berte et Dominici iugalium, qui hanc cartulam
                        offersionis tradiderunt in manu <persName key="#Monks #Offersio/donatio"
                                ><name ref="Hugo">Ugonis</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monachi</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monks" ref="#juridical_persons/2076">Sancte Elene</orgName>
                        in iusu ecclesie Sancti Cipriani, et hanc cartulam fieri rogaverunt ut
                        supra. Rogati autem sunt <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Stantius"
                            >Stancion</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Specialized_workers #Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name
                                ref="Dominicus/faber">Dominicus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Specialized_workers">faber</rs>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Aribrandus/de Laurentia"
                                >Ariprandus</name></persName> de Laurentia, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Iohannes/de sancta Maria"
                                >Iohannes</name></persName> de Sancta Maria, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Iohannes/Bonus/de Menegella"
                                >Iohannes Bonus</name></persName> de Menegella et reliqui. </ab>
                </div>
